name: 6Hundred
description:
commemorative piece to celebrate @delir1umNFT's <600 followers> achieved on Twitter. 600 ed. with a very low price to spread my respect for all the people who has supported me all this time. 

total thanks to those who are part of this. hoping to give more beauties for your collection. it's unbelievable how fast we made it here. my last days weren't easy. lot of stuff in my head. 

ly.
